OL,3,CLyndon Farnham faces further
OL,4,Cchallenges as he picks new top team
OL,6,FBut already, there are challenges to
OL,7,Fthat harmony.
OL,9,FDeputy David Warr, the current Housing
OL,10,FMinister, has told ITV News he will
OL,11,Fput himself forward to stay in his
OL,12,Fjob, contesting the nomination of
OL,13,FReform Leader Sam Mezec.
OL,15,FAnd there is a rumour that Deputy
OL,16,FHelen Miles may try to remain as Home
OL,17,FAffairs Minister - setting up a fight
OL,18,Fwith Deputy Mary Le Hegarat.
