OL,3,CLyndon Farnham faces further
OL,4,Cchallenges as he picks new top team
OL,6,FThose are just the immediate battles,
OL,7,Ffurther down the line Lyndon Farnham
OL,8,Ffaces greater complications.
OL,10,FReform Jersey are deeply committed to
OL,11,Ftheir centre-left political vision
OL,12,Fthat won them ten seats in the 2022
OL,13,Felection.
OL,15,FLast week, their leader told me that
OL,16,Fif they find themselves "obstructed or
OL,17,Foverruled" then "there would be no
OL,18,Fpoint in us carrying on" in government.
