OL,3,CLyndon Farnham faces further
OL,4,Cchallenges as he picks new top team
OL,6,FAnd of course, the biggest winner from
OL,7,Fthese picks is Deputy Tom Binet. He is
OL,8,Fnot only given the job of running
OL,9,Fhealth and the hospital project, but
OL,10,Falso the Deputy Chief Minister role -
OL,11,Fsome reward for calling the vote of no
OL,12,Fconfidence in Kristina Moore.
OL,14,FHe is known for being straight talking
OL,15,Fand unafraid to make his views heard
OL,16,Fand is now one of the most powerful
OL,17,Fpoliticians in the assembly.
