OL,3,CLyndon Farnham faces further
OL,4,Cchallenges as he picks new top team
OL,6,FBut he also brought down the previous
OL,7,Fgovernment because he was unhappy
OL,8,Fabout its state - a warning to the
OL,9,Fisland's new leader.
OL,11,FThe last government fell because of
OL,12,Finfighting in the top team and a style
OL,13,Fof management that caused a lot of
OL,14,Fdissatisfaction, now it is Lyndon
OL,15,FFarnham's turn to show if he can do
OL,16,Fany better.
